overview: Mankind will soon face its greatest enemy and only by reforming the D.O.L.L. Squad can Lady Lazurus stop the impending destruction. But first, she must have her granddaughter read the files of the paranormal women who will make up the D.O.L.L.. Squad. Learn who Topaz, Nightwitch and Patriot Girl are and see them overcome their diabolical enemies.
tagline: Learn who Topaz, Nightwitch and Patriot Girl are and see them overcome their diabolical enemies.
title: Codename D.O.L.L. Squad
